        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: June 15, 2024</p>
        
        <p><strong>Al Ishaat: Islamic Audio Library</strong> (the "App") is a free service. This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>We do not collect any personally identifiable information. The App uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. These include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Google Play Services</li>
            <li>Firebase Analytics</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>The App uses <strong>Room Database</strong> to save your offline preferences and downloaded content locally on your device. This data is not uploaded to any server.</p>

        <h2>3. Media and Internet Access</h2>
        <p>The App requires Internet access to stream audio content and uses <strong>Media3 ExoPlayer</strong> for playback. We do not track your listening history on our servers.</p>

        <h2>4. Permissions</h2>
        <p>The App may request <strong>Storage/Media</strong> permissions solely to save and play downloaded audio files for offline use.</p>

        <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> absalamofficial.cmyk@gmail.com</p>
